---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="BNS BNSS BSA - New Criminal Laws Privacy Policy - Logicpath Systems">
    <section class="legal-page" style="padding-top: 120px; min-height: 100vh;">
        <div class="container reveal">
            <div class="glass-card" style="padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);">
                <header style="margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center;">
                    <h1 class="gradient-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);"><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 25, 2025</p>
                </header>

                <main class="legal-content">
                    <p><strong>LogicPath Systems</strong> ("we", "our", or "us") built the <strong>BNS BNSS BSA - New Criminal Laws</strong> app ("App") as a free, ad-supported educational tool. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use our App.</p>
                    
                    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                    <p>This Privacy Policy is meant to help you understand what information we collect, why we collect it, and how you can manage your information. By using the App, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.</p>

                    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>We do <strong>NOT</strong> directly collect, store, or transmit any personal data to our servers. The App operates primarily offline. Specifically:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>No user accounts or login required</li>
                        <li>No names, email addresses, or phone numbers collected</li>
                        <li>No location data accessed</li>
                        <li>No cameras, microphone, or contacts accessed</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>3. Locally Stored Data</h2>
                    <p>The App stores the following data <strong>locally on your device</strong> using SharedPreferences:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Bookmarks</strong> — sections you save for quick access</li>
                        <li><strong>Personal notes</strong> — your annotations on sections</li>
                        <li><strong>Quiz progress</strong> — scores, XP, streaks, levels, and badges</li>
                        <li><strong>Recently viewed sections</strong> — for your convenience</li>
                        <li><strong>Theme preference</strong> — light, dark, or system</li>
                        <li><strong>Recent searches</strong> — your search history</li>
                    </ul>
                    <blockquote style="border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-primary); padding-left: 1rem; margin-left: 0; color: var(--text-secondary); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 4px;">
                        <strong>This data never leaves your device</strong> and is not accessible to us or any third party.
                    </blockquote>

                    <h2>4. Advertisements</h2>
                    <p>The App displays advertisements through <strong>Google AdMob</strong> to support ongoing development. AdMob may collect certain information automatically, including:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Device identifiers (Advertising ID)</li>
                        <li>IP address</li>
                        <li>General location (country/region level, not precise)</li>
                        <li>App usage data and interaction with ads</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Google AdMob's data practices are governed by <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--accent-secondary);">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
                    <p>You can opt out of personalized advertising by:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Visiting your device's <strong>Settings &gt; Google &gt; Ads</strong> and enabling "Opt out of Ads Personalization"</li>
                        <li>Or visiting <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--accent-secondary);">Google's Ad Settings</a></li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>5. Permissions</h2>
                    <p>The App may request the following device permissions:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Internet</strong> — required for loading advertisements</li>
                        <li><strong>Text-to-Speech</strong> — to read sections aloud (uses your device's built-in TTS engine)</li>
                        <li><strong>Share</strong> — to share section text via your device's share sheet</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>No camera, microphone, contacts, or storage permissions are required.</p>

                    <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
                    <p>The App integrates the following third-party services:</p>
                    <div style="overflow-x: auto;">
                        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">Service</th>
                                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">Purpose</th>
                                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">Privacy Policy</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Google AdMob</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Displaying advertisements</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);"><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--accent-secondary);">Link</a></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Google Mobile Ads SDK</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Ad delivery and mediation</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);"><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--accent-secondary);">Link</a></td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    <p>Google Fonts used in the App are bundled within the app package and do <strong>not</strong> make network requests.</p>

                    <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
                    <p>The App is suitable for all ages. We do not knowingly collect any personal information from anyone, including children under the age of 13. The ads displayed are configured to comply with Google's policies for family-friendly content.</p>

                    <h2>8. Data Deletion</h2>
                    <p>Since all user data is stored locally on your device, you can delete it at any time by:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Clearing the app data from your device <strong>Settings &gt; Apps &gt; BNS BNSS BSA &gt; Clear Data</strong></li>
                        <li>Uninstalling the App</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>No residual data will remain on any server as we do not operate any user-data servers.</p>

                    <h2>9. Data Security</h2>
                    <p>We value your trust. While we do not collect personal data on our servers, we ensure that:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>All locally stored data remains on your device</li>
                        <li>The App does not transmit your bookmarks, notes, or quiz progress anywhere</li>
                        <li>Ad-related data collection by Google AdMob follows Google's security standards</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in the App with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

                    <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
                    <p><strong>LogicPath Systems</strong><br>
                    📧 Email: <a href="mailto:contact@logicpathsystems.com" style="color: var(--accent-secondary);">contact@logicpathsystems.com</a></p>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;"><em>This privacy policy is effective as of June 25, 2025.</em></p>
                </main>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .legal-content h2 {
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .legal-content p, .legal-content ul, .legal-content table {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .legal-content ul {
        padding-left: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .legal-content li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
</style>
